575
00:36:33,490 --> 00:36:36,900
Don't sit with stern faces like this.

576
00:36:37,700 --> 00:36:39,230
Go, go.

577
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:41,350
You're stressing me out, too.

578
00:36:42,110 --> 00:36:43,730
Go clear things up, okay?

579
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,720
Go.

580
00:36:45,810 --> 00:36:47,770
Please, Itthi and Ritt.

581
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:50,230
Be nice to each other.

582
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,360
Go. Talk to each other.

583
00:36:55,590 --> 00:36:57,740
Take a rest. No talking.

584
00:36:59,830 --> 00:37:00,540
Thank you so much

585
00:37:00,820 --> 00:37:01,820
