589
00:37:16,640 --> 00:37:17,440
And...

590
00:37:18,850 --> 00:37:20,140
Are you going back?

591
00:37:21,390 --> 00:37:22,390
Would you like a ride?

592
00:37:23,620 --> 00:37:24,500
That's fine.

593
00:37:25,010 --> 00:37:26,010
