any misunderstandings with you.

597
00:37:46,990 --> 00:37:48,210
The car is right on time.

598
00:37:50,950 --> 00:37:53,000
Let's catch up later.

599
00:38:17,840 --> 00:38:18,840
Here comes tomorrow.

600
00:38:20,740 --> 00:38:21,970
In a few hours,

601
00:38:23,010 --> 00:38:24,710
