602
00:38:29,150 --> 00:38:30,310
I'm not going to leave you.

603
00:38:31,930 --> 00:38:34,110
I should be happy

604
00:38:34,920 --> 00:38:36,690
for you to follow your dream, right?

605
00:38:38,140 --> 00:38:39,620
It'll be better

606
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:41,800
if you're

607
00:38:42,120 --> 00:38:43,470
in my dream.

608
00:38:44,510 --> 00:38:45,930
Whoa,

609
00:38:46,730 --> 00:38:47,730
even when you're leaving,

610
00:38:48,370 --> 00:38:50,470
you're still saying
sweet things to keep my hopes up, huh?

611
00:39:01,010 --> 00:39:02,120
Thank you so much

612
00:39:03,570 --> 00:39:04,920
for always being beside me.

613
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:11,770
After this,

614
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:15,290
