615
00:39:17,300 --> 00:39:18,790
Magic Move without you.

616
00:40:33,090 --> 00:40:34,090
Don't cry.

617
00:40:35,530 --> 00:40:36,480
Who's crying?

618
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,000
No one's crying.

619
00:40:39,640 --> 00:40:41,870
