620
00:40:48,540 --> 00:40:49,840
Can you please help me pack?

621
00:40:49,930 --> 00:40:51,220
You ruined my cool vibe.

622
00:40:58,620 --> 00:41:01,110
You two, come closer, please.

623
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:10,890
Thank you so much

624
00:41:12,130 --> 00:41:15,870
for bearing with me for your whole lives.

625
00:41:17,000 --> 00:41:18,900
Thank you so much.

626
00:41:22,310 --> 00:41:23,400
Itthi,

627
00:41:26,100 --> 00:41:29,910
please take care of our family business

628
00:41:30,830 --> 00:41:36,560
