639
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,350
Chinese Ghost Festival,

640
00:42:32,390 --> 00:42:34,120
or Chinese New Year.

641
00:42:35,060 --> 00:42:37,590
Both the stuffed dough pyramid
and the Chinese New Year's cake,

642
00:42:39,450 --> 00:42:41,710
I like them all.

643
00:42:43,810 --> 00:42:46,680
I'll look forward to eating them up there.

644
00:42:48,540 --> 00:42:52,070
Don't let me wait for so long that
I have to remind you myself.

645
00:43:45,300 --> 00:43:46,810
Endeavor

646
