647
00:43:51,560 --> 00:43:52,920
Give your heart to it, okay?

648
00:43:53,660 --> 00:43:55,180
Do your best.

649
00:43:56,240 --> 00:43:57,920
I believe that my son

650
00:43:58,450 --> 00:43:59,600
