651
00:44:04,100 --> 00:44:05,100
Yes, Mom.

652
00:44:07,500 --> 00:44:08,690
Good luck, dear.

653
00:44:12,630 --> 00:44:13,400
Yes, Mom.

654
00:44:16,770 --> 00:44:18,190
