After you finish changing,
come to pay respect to Grandpa here, okay?

670
00:45:50,360 --> 00:45:51,040
Yes.

671
00:46:51,250 --> 00:46:53,480
Thank you so much for coming

672
00:46:53,910 --> 00:46:55,810
