699
00:48:22,000 --> 00:48:22,520
Yes.

700
00:48:23,270 --> 00:48:24,020
Sure.

701
00:48:30,540 --> 00:48:31,800
You're going to study further

702
00:48:32,510 --> 00:48:33,610
